# .driverignore — driver selection for Nitrogen
#
# Format: gitignore‑style path patterns.
# Directories listed here are EXCLUDED from the build.
# Infrastructure modules (pci, driver_api, driver_context, …) are
# always included and should never appear here.
#
# Example — exclude wireless and Bluetooth:
# iwlwifi/
# bluetooth/

# USB subsystem (xhci, ehci, msd, hub, …). Uncomment to exclude:
# usb/

# Intel wireless. Uncomment to exclude:
# iwlwifi/

# Realtek SD card reader. Uncomment to exclude:
# storage/

# Audio (HDA). Uncomment to exclude:
# hda/
